### 🚀 SafeAI Proxy – Full Flow Test (SECURE VERSION)

### =====================================

### 1️⃣ יצירת פרופיל

### =====================================

POST http://localhost:3001/profiles
Content-Type: application/json

{
"name": "test-profile",
"allowedCategories": ["code"],
"blockedCategories": ["violence"],
"createdBy": "admin",
"creatorEmail": "[admin@test.com](mailto:admin@test.com)",
"contentPrompts": ["You are a coding assistant."],
"behaviorPrompts": ["Answer only technical questions."]
}

### 👉 שמרי את:

### response.body._id → {{profileId}}

### =====================================

### 2️⃣ יצירת משתמש (BYOK)

### =====================================

POST http://localhost:3001/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
"email": "test@test.com",
"profileId": "69a80a2128be7b3daa47622b",
"mode": "BYOK"
}

### 👉 שמרי:

### response.body.user._id → {{userId}}

### response.body.proxyApiKey → {{proxyKey}}

### ⚠️ שימי לב:

### זה הפעם היחידה שתראי את ה-key

### =====================================

### 3️⃣ הוספת Provider Key (יוצפן אוטומטית)

### =====================================

POST http://localhost:3001/provider-keys
Content-Type: application/json

{
"userId": "69ba6ea3e7d80f3d538f8a7c",
"provider": "openai",
"apiKey": "your_key_here"
}
### 👉 לא יוחזר apiKey — רק metadata

### =====================================

### 4️⃣ בדיקת Proxy (תקין)

### =====================================

POST http://localhost:3001/v1/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer your_proxy_key_here

{
"model": "gpt-5-mini",
"messages": [
{
"role": "user",
"content": "Write a simple JavaScript function"
}
]
}

### =====================================

### 5️⃣ בדיקת חסימה (פילטר)

### =====================================

POST http://localhost:3001/v1/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{proxyKey}}

{
"model": "gpt-4o-mini",
"messages": [
{
"role": "user",
"content": "bad content test"
}
]
}

### =====================================

### 6️⃣ בדיקת prefix model (מומלץ!)

### =====================================

POST http://localhost:3001/v1/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{proxyKey}}

{
"model": "openai/gpt-4o-mini",
"messages": [
{
"role": "user",
"content": "Write a function"
}
]
}

### =====================================

### 7️⃣ שליפת משתמשים (ללא secrets)

### =====================================

GET http://localhost:3001/users

### =====================================

### 8️⃣ שליפת פרופילים

### =====================================

GET http://localhost:3001/profiles
